</table>
<h4><span class="mw-headline" id="Confederate_militia">Confederate militia</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Militia_(United_States)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=18" title="Edit section: Confederate militia">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h4>
<p>The most important:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Arkansas_Militia_in_the_Civil_War" title="Arkansas Militia in the Civil War">Arkansas Militia</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Missouri_State_Guard" title="Missouri State Guard">Missouri State Guard</a></li>
</ul>
<table class="plainlinks metadata ambox mbox-small-left ambox-content" role="presentation">
<tr>
