<div class="thumbinner" style="width:162px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Ludlow-miliitia.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/1/1c/Ludlow-miliitia.jpg/160px-Ludlow-miliitia.jpg" width="160" height="103" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/1/1c/Ludlow-miliitia.jpg/240px-Ludlow-miliitia.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/1/1c/Ludlow-miliitia.jpg/320px-Ludlow-miliitia.jpg 2x" data-file-width="460" data-file-height="296" /></a>
